{"tid":1827531,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"另一半太優秀 會唔會自卑？","createTime":"2020-01-17T04:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T08:11:39.000Z","uid":204568,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"360f0d7415964d2a4aa8f372f638286347115fbc","tid":1827531,"uid":204568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"初初都唔知佢屋企背景 <br />\n淨係知佢係英國留學 <br />\n有次送佢番屋企 見到係豪宅區 <br />\n先知同佢差區有幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n種種潮文係我腦中一閃而過<br />\ncome on james <br />\n我都唔敢問佢介唔介意<br />\n<br />\n有同自己講過要努力 <br />\n奈何佢所有方面都比我叻比我優秀 <br />\n我諗係佢細細個就開始培養 <br />\n彈琴跳舞溜冰咩都識 <br />\n仲要讀緊神科 <br />\n<br />\n講才華我又唔夠 <br />\n講讀書又唔夠佢叻<br />\n講將來吸金能力又唔夠佢比<br />\n講家底更加無得比 <br />\n<br />\n有時諗諗下都有種 拖累佢既感覺"},{"pid":"5c3d7de79afa10fd3131f9c81a27ef8bfb081c94","tid":1827531,"uid":187187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"咁你諗唔諗住結婚?"},{"pid":"cbf04a206f179dec0d4799ee30173935c4bc6fed","tid":1827531,"uid":204568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c3d7de79afa10fd3131f9c81a27ef8bfb081c94","tid":1827531,"uid":187187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"咁你諗唔諗住結婚?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"我當然想 但未見過家長<br />\n唔知有無壓力"},{"pid":"2ccba117f8eca1ac1dfcd1d6424d98ff196c2bc6","tid":1827531,"uid":30751,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:37:13.000Z","msg":"咁佢都肯同你一齊啦<br />\n一齊左好耐？"},{"pid":"3cf2144af35b5f10155e73be3e016049954be804","tid":1827531,"uid":316596,"like":54,"dislike":7,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"人廢就自然自卑<br />\n有啲野不嬲都係咁死<br />\n唔同起跑線自然有唔同發展<br />\n<br />\n事實上你要一個零家底嘅人發大達做李嘉誠二世<br />\n根本係痴人說夢<br />\n<br />\n但你要一個零家底嘅人 讀好書做醫生<br />\n就非不可為<br />\n<br />\n但如果你自己零家底 起跑線差<br />\n就自艾自怨 講到好似全世界迫害你 欠左你<br />\n而忽略左每一年都有公屋 單親人士 <br />\n讀到Law 讀到MBBS 成功從商 成功做到社會top 10%時<br />\n<br />\n上面提到嘅所有人<br />\n拍埋你條女到 可能都係冇家底嘅人 可能搵嘅錢都侒冇得比<br />\n但至少佢地「唔需要」自卑<br />\n自卑係自己揀 你可以發達到李嘉誠咁都可以自卑<br />\n你自覺自己係廢人 就可以自卑<br />\n最緊要睇到自己嘅Values姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本就同外界冇關<br />\n<br />\n不過你係應該要自卑<br />\n因為你智商太低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff929370f3c1783291315c5c5e9e3f75e270ce6","tid":1827531,"uid":204568,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"2ccba117f8eca1ac1dfcd1d6424d98ff196c2bc6","tid":1827531,"uid":30751,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:37:13.000Z","msg":"咁佢都肯同你一齊啦<br />\n一齊左好耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:38:17.000Z","msg":"唔耐 兩個月"},{"pid":"51fa363c12f6713b43b7fe578bdbc0eb0a267f7f","tid":1827531,"uid":21664,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"拍拖姐 結婚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拍到咁上下先算啦"},{"pid":"988789d27ff32bc2dc3b9ef8205a73425f266d65","tid":1827531,"uid":59395,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:43:44.000Z","msg":"咪撚拖累人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申窮矮柒毒肥"},{"pid":"18ddcee3a0631145ea9c7474e14814ec97cf5232","tid":1827531,"uid":187187,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"51fa363c12f6713b43b7fe578bdbc0eb0a267f7f","tid":1827531,"uid":21664,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"拍拖姐 結婚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拍到咁上下先算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:58:23.000Z","msg":"咪係 樓主諗惦下個月情人節點先啦"},{"pid":"104d2811b75a345cfaace2169b39407c156b5b42","tid":1827531,"uid":30751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ff929370f3c1783291315c5c5e9e3f75e270ce6","tid":1827531,"uid":204568,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"2ccba117f8eca1ac1dfcd1d6424d98ff196c2bc6","tid":1827531,"uid":30751,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-